node.text: PLANKING - A simple yet effective exercise I fell in love with! I’ll plank on IGlive at 6pm daily, till the circuit breaker period is over. Just 2 minutes each time, join in as my virtual plank buddies! 👋🏼
@ytravelworldwide thank you! Give it a try maybe?
@avchiang You have such good form too - totally level. Very impressive. 👏  I can plank ... for seconds. 😂😂
@yesstilltalking thank you so much! I’m sure you can plank 1sec more each day!
Wow! You are a plank machine. Bravo! 🙌👏👏👏
“Just 2 minutes” girl I can barely do 30 seconds 😂
stay strong, stay safe, keep the motivation going, love team ooszoo ❤❤❤🥇
